text:
Just learned it earlier, but...
Hinana-chan was already able to do it...

Ah, yeah...!
I was just checking over what we learned today...

Is that so~? Koito-chan, even though you just learned
it today during the lesson, you were already able to do it.

Eh...?
I-I wonder if that's true?

Hmm~ Well, today Toru-senpai and
the others weren't here for extra lessons, so...

Hinana and Koito-chan 
eem to be a bit ahead, right?

But everyone still hasn't arrived~
Maybe their extra lessons haven't finished yet?

Ah... um, w-well, there's still a bit
of time until our scheduled time...!

Hey, Koito-chan,
what do you want to do for the unit live~?

You'll probably be asked again today about
what you want to do for the unit live.
